                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9403" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1410</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1084 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破旧立新，大有“作”为：初创HL化工企业成本核算破局之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Break then stand, enormous to “act”: The way of cost accounting for start-up HL chemical enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汪方军，安康，张洲豪，许硕磊，任浠雨，吴思锐，任奇巨</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中化学华陆新材料有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">23 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作业成本法；成本核算；化工企业；初创企业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Activity-Based Costing; Cost Accounting; Chemical Industry Enterprise; Startup Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在外部经济压力和国内政策变革的双重影响下，化工行业正面临转型挑战，特别是向战略性新兴产业拓展。化工企业采用传统的完全成本法进行成本核算，已无法反映新兴化工产业的产品品种多、批量小、生产流程复杂、间接成本高和研发投入大等特点。面对产业结构升级和市场竞争加剧的双重压力，中国化工企业迫切需要新的核算体系来落实精细化管理。
本案例研究了作业成本计算法在HL化工企业生产气凝胶新产品时的成本核算应用。通过实地调研，我们梳理了现有的完全成本法核算过程，发现其在成本核算中存在的问题及其成因。基于成本核算的特性，经过分析其必要性和可行性，我们选择了作业成本法计算新产品成本。作业成本法以生产流程（作业）为基础，考虑了不同产品的开发与生产差异，适合新兴化工产品的成本核算需求。
考虑到气凝胶新产品处于全生命周期的引入期，具有强烈的创新属性和高研发成本，本案例在成本核算中纳入了研发费用，并将其计入最终产品成本。在整合产品类别、梳理生产流程、确认资源消耗、划分作业中心、分析成本动因基础上，我们计算了气凝胶新产品的作业成本，并与传统完全成本法的成本结果进行了比较分析，揭示了不同产品成本差异的原因。
实施作业成本计算与管理体系后，HL公司的成本管理效率和经济效益显著提高。准确的成本信息为公司提供了研发和生产决策的依据，是企业在初创期获得坚实竞争优势的重要支撑。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Under the dual impact of external economic pressures and domestic policy changes, the chemical industry is facing transformation challenges, particularly in expanding into strategic emerging industries. Chemical companies that continue using traditional full-cost accounting methods are unable to accurately reflect the characteristics of the emerging chemical sector, such as the diversity of products, small batch sizes, complex production processes, high indirect costs, and significant research and development (R&amp;D) investment. Faced with the dual pressures of industrial upgrading and intensified market competition, Chinese chemical companies urgently need a new accounting system to implement refined management.
This case study examines the application of activity-based costing (ABC) in HL Chemical&#39;s cost accounting for its new aerogel product. Through field research, we reviewed the current full-cost accounting process and identified the problems and underlying causes. Based on the characteristics of cost accounting, after analyzing the necessity and feasibility, we selected the ABC method to calculate the cost of the new product. ABC, which is based on production processes (activities), takes into account the differences in product development and production, making it suitable for the cost accounting needs of emerging chemical products.
Considering that the new aerogel product is in the introduction phase of its lifecycle, with strong innovation attributes and high R&amp;D costs, this case study incorporated R&amp;D expenses into the final product cost. By consolidating product categories, streamlining production processes, confirming resource consumption, defining activity centers, and analyzing cost drivers, we calculated the activity costs for the new aerogel product and compared them with the results from traditional full-cost accounting, revealing the reasons for the cost differences between different products.
After implementing the activity-based costing and management system, HL&#39;s cost management efficiency and economic performance significantly improved. Accurate cost information provided a basis for R&amp;D and production decision-making, serving as a crucial support for the company to gain a strong competitive advantage during its early development stages.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作业成本法；完全成本法；成本核算；成本管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
